---
import DefaultLayout from '@/layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';
---

<DefaultLayout activeLinkIndex={0} title="Home">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1 class="intro__title">
      Markdown으로 기록하고
      <br />
      Astro로 빌드하는 블로그 템플릿입니다.
    </h1>

    <div class="intro__description">
      <p>
        주제와 날짜, 두 가지 방식으로
        <br />
        기록의 흐름을 살펴볼 수 있습니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="card-group" aria-labelledby="card-group-title">
    <h2 id="card-group-title" class="sr-only">글 탐색</h2>

    <a href="/archive" class="card">
      <h3 class="card__title">주제별</h3>
      <p class="card__description">
        목차에 작성한 순서대로
        <br />
        글을 주제별로 묶어 보여줍니다.
      </p>
      <span class="card__button">주제별 보기 </span>
    </a>

    <a href="/latest" class="card">
      <h3 class="card__title">날짜별</h3>
      <p class="card__description">
        날짜를 기준으로
        <br />
        최신 글 순으로 보여줍니다.
      </p>
      <span class="card__button">날짜별 보기 </span>
    </a>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout>

<style lang="scss">
  .intro {
    padding: $space-12 0;

    @include media-down('md') {
      padding: $space-10 0;
    }

    @include media-down('sm') {
      padding: $space-8 0;
    }

    &__title {
      font-size: $font-size-32;

      @include media-down('md') {
        font-size: $font-size-26;
      }

      @include media-down('sm') {
        font-size: $font-size-24;
      }
    }

    &__description {
      padding-top: $space-8;

      @include media-down('md') {
        padding-top: $space-6;
      }

      p + p {
        margin-top: $space-4;

        @include media-down('sm') {
          margin-top: $space-3;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .card-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: $space-8;
    padding: $space-12 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);

    @include media-down('md') {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: $space-6;
      padding: $space-10 0;
    }

    @include media-down('sm') {
      padding: $space-8 0;
    }
  }

  .card {
    $self: &;

    display: flex;
    flex: 1 1 0;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-width: 0;
    min-height: 19rem;
    padding: $space-8 $space-9;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    transition: all $transition-duration-1;

    @include media-down('md') {
      min-height: 15rem;
      padding: $space-6;
    }

    @include media-down('sm') {
      min-height: 12rem;
      padding: $space-5;
    }

    &__title {
      font-size: $font-size-24;

      @include media-down('sm') {
        font-size: $font-size-22;
      }
    }

    &__description {
      margin-top: $space-3;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: $font-size-15;
    }

    &__button {
      align-self: flex-start;
      margin-top: auto;
      padding: $space-2 $space-4;
      background: var(--text-heading);
      color: var(--bg-surface);
      font-weight: $font-weight-bold;
      font-size: $font-size-14;
      transition: all $transition-duration-1;

      &:hover {
        background-color: var(--accent);
      }
    }

    &:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px color-mix(in srgb, var(--text-body) 10%, transparent);

      #{$self}__button {
        background-color: var(--accent);
        transform: translateX(2px);
      }
    }
  }
</style>
